2010;;Basement;;British;;Asham Kamboj;;Danny Dyer, Jimi Mistry, Emily Beecham;;horror;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Basement_(2010_film);;After returning from an anti-war demonstration, Gary (Danny Dyer), Sarah (Kierston Wareing), Saffron (Lois Winstone), Pru (Emily Beecham) and Derek (Jimi Mistry) stop in the country. Derek and Saffron discover a metal hatch in the middle of the forest and they decide to explore inside. Gary, Pru and Sarah search for their missing friends and follow them into the hatch and find themselves locked in when it closes behind them.